      "parentId": "{7C0CA751-F2C2-4D9B-A423-C5B31E03B570}",
      "title": "Practical Operator Workflow",
      "body": "# 6.1 Practical Operator Workflow\r\n\r\n<table class=\"doc-table\">\r\n<tr><th>Stage</th><th>Operator action</th><th>Expected result</th></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Prepare</td><td>check source</td><td>set clean target</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Run</td><td>select options</td><td>start conversion</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Open</td><td>load FMX project</td><td>build in Delphi</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Validate</td><td>run app</td><td>exercise real workflows</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Refine</td><td>improve converter</td><td>rerun cleanly</td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n1. Prepare a clean output directory.\r\n2. Run the converter against the selected VCL project.\r\n3. Open the generated FMX project in Delphi.\r\n4. Resolve structural and compile issues first.",
      "status": "Ready",
